syntax:
abstract int
fact duplicable int

exclusive data tree a = 
  | Leaf
  | Node { left: tree a; right: tree a; size: a }

val rec tree_size (consumes x: tree unknown): (int | x @ tree int) =
  match explain x with
  | Leaf ->
      1
  | Node { left; right } ->
      let l = tree_size left in
      let r = tree_size right in
      let total = l + r + 1 in
      x.size <- total;
      total
  end
